A high-fidelity macro studio product visualization cross-section cutaway of a modular flight suit leg armor sleeve panel. The outermost 1.5mm active chameleon stealth skin consists of a flexible transparent polyurethanic hydrogel layer patterned with micro-etched horizontal channel rows holding suspended 130nm green guanine nanocrystals. Directly beneath rests an amber-colored 1.0mm triboelectric fluoropolymer mesh. The structural core shows a dense 10.0mm matte-black carbon fiber polycarbonate weave showing embedded continuous graphene ground lines. The innermost face features a compliant, deep teal-colored internal lining sleeve, realistic studio overhead cross-lighting, photorealistic material and resin textures, 8k --ar 16:9
